{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/(main)/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/page,_N_T_/learn/prompt/developer"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level/__PAGE__","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type","/!KG1haW4p/learn","/!KG1haW4p","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0.q-h669a_dqa.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.16t1db8_9y2o~.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn7g3rv..css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14uv9l3-k2qh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/16sk4~vc8e6sh.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0c9ih0_ge37cg.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-02v2juswviadt.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Prompt 工程进阶教程 - AI工具市场</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"学习 Prompt 工程 的进阶知识\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\"><header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white text-sm\">⚡</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">AI 工具市场</span></div></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"relative w-72\"><div class=\"relative\"><svg class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"全局搜索...\" class=\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div></div><a class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"学院\" href=\"/learn\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">🎓</span></a><a href=\"http://hsinky.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"个人博客\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📰</span></a></div></div></header><div class=\"flex\"><aside class=\"w-72 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col fixed left-0 top-14 h-[calc(100vh-56px)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/developer\">开发者路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">Prompt 工程</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Prompt 工程</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">高级 Prompt 工程技术</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->90分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>开发者路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/prompt/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/prompt/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/prompt/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>结构化输出与数据提取</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3 text-blue-700\">为什么需要结构化输出？</h4><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">程序处理结构化数据（JSON）比处理自由文本更可靠。要求 AI 以 JSON 格式输出，可以：</p><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 自动解析结果</li><li>• 验证数据完整性</li><li>• 存储到数据库</li><li>• 传递给下游服务</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">实战：提取结构化数据</h4><div class=\"font-mono text-sm\"><pre>分析以下文本，以 JSON 格式返回提取的信息：\n\n## 输入文本\n张明，32岁，软件工程师，工作于北京字节跳动，邮箱：zhangming@email.com\n\n## 输出格式（严格遵守）\n{\n  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;姓名&quot;,\n  &quot;age&quot;: 年龄(数字),\n  &quot;profession&quot;: &quot;职业&quot;,\n  &quot;company&quot;: &quot;公司全称&quot;,\n  &quot;location&quot;: {\n    &quot;city&quot;: &quot;城市&quot;,\n    &quot;country&quot;: &quot;国家&quot;\n  },\n  &quot;email&quot;: &quot;邮箱地址&quot;,\n  &quot;confidence&quot;: 置信度0-1之间的数字\n}\n\n## 要求\n- 不要返回任何解释文字\n- 不要添加 Markdown 代码块标记（如 ```json）\n- 如果某个信息无法提取，该字段设为 null\n- 置信度表示你对该提取结果的把握程度</pre></div></div><div class=\"bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-yellow-800\">解析代码示例</h4><div class=\"font-mono text-sm\"><pre>const response = await callAI(prompt);\nconst data = JSON.parse(response);\n\n// 验证数据\nif (!data.name || !data.email) {\n  throw new Error(&#x27;Required fields missing&#x27;);\n}\n\n// 使用数据\nconsole.log(`${data.name} 工作于 ${data.company}`);</pre></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>Few-Shot Learning：用示例教会 AI</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3 text-green-700\">Few-Shot 的威力</h4><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">提供几个示例，比写一页说明更有效。示例帮助 AI 理解：</p><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 期望的输出格式</li><li>• 应该保留哪些信息</li><li>• 语言风格和语气</li><li>• 隐式的规则（不用明说）</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">示例：情感分析 Few-Shot</h4><div class=\"font-mono text-sm\"><pre>判断以下文本的情感倾向（正面/负面/中性），并给出置信度。\n\n## 示例\n示例 1：\n输入：这个产品太好用了，强烈推荐！\n输出：\n{\n  &quot;sentiment&quot;: &quot;正面&quot;,\n  &quot;confidence&quot;: 0.95,\n  &quot;reasons&quot;: [&quot;太好用了&quot;, &quot;强烈推荐&quot;]\n}\n\n示例 2：\n输入：还行吧，没什么特别的。\n输出：\n{\n  &quot;sentiment&quot;: &quot;中性&quot;,\n  &quot;confidence&quot;: 0.80,\n  &quot;reasons&quot;: []\n}\n\n示例 3：\n输入：质量很差，再也不买了！\n输出：\n{\n  &quot;sentiment&quot;: &quot;负面&quot;,\n  &quot;confidence&quot;: 0.92,\n  &quot;reasons&quot;: [&quot;质量很差&quot;, &quot;再也不买了&quot;]\n}\n\n## 待分析\n输入：服务态度很好，但物流太慢了。\n输出：</pre></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-700\">Few-Shot 最佳实践</h4><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1\"><li>• 提供 3-5 个示例即可，更多不一定更好</li><li>• 示例要覆盖不同场景（正面、负面、中性）</li><li>• 示例格式要和待分析内容一致</li><li>• 复杂任务使用多样性示例，简单任务用一致性示例</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>高级推理技巧</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">1. Self-Consistency（自洽性采样）</h4><div class=\"bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">让模型生成多个推理路径，选择最一致的答案：</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm mb-3\"><p>对于需要逻辑推理的问题：</p><p>1. 让模型生成 5 个不同的推理过程</p><p>2. 比较这 5 个过程的结论</p><p>3. 选择出现最多的结论作为最终答案</p></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">成本：5x，但准确率显著提升</p></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">2. Tree of Thoughts（树状思考）</h4><div class=\"bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">探索多个可能的分支，像树的分支一样展开：</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm\"><p>问题：如何提高用户留存率？</p><p class=\"mt-2\">- 方案A：改进产品功能</p><p>  - 能：提升核心体验</p><p>  - 不能：可能需要大量开发</p><p>  - 预期效果：🌟🌟🌟🌟⭐</p><p class=\"mt-2\">- 方案B：增加用户激励</p><p>  - 能：短效激励</p><p>  - 不能：可能被滥用</p><p>  - 预期效果：🌟🌟🌟⭐⭐</p><p class=\"mt-2\">- 方案C：优化用户引导</p><p>  - 能：改善首印象</p><p>  - 不能：对老用户无效</p><p>  - 预期效果：🌟🌟🌟⭐</p><p class=\"mt-2 font-semibold\">推荐：方案A（综合评分最高）</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">4</span>RAG Prompt 设计</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-emerald-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3 text-emerald-700\">RAG（检索增强）场景的 Prompt 特殊性</h4><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">RAG 场景下，你需要让 AI 仅基于检索到的内容回答，而不是使用训练数据：</p></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"font-mono text-sm\"><pre>你是公司的内部知识助手。\n\n# 检索到的相关文档（请仅基于以下内容回答）\n\n【文档1】\n公司假期政策：员工每年享有15天年假，需提前7天申请。年假不可跨年使用。\n\n【文档2】\n病假规定：员工每年有5天带薪病假，需提供医院证明。病假可累计跨年。\n\n【文档3】\n事假规定：事假按天扣除薪资，每月最多3天。\n\n# 你的任务\n\n基于【检索到的相关文档】回答用户问题。\n\n# 重要约束\n\n1. 答案必须严格基于【检索到的相关文档】\n2. 如果文档中没有相关信息，明确告知：&quot;文档中没有这方面的信息&quot;\n3. 不要使用你的训练数据中的通用知识\n4. 回答时注明信息来源，如&quot;根据文档1...&quot;\n5. 如果多个文档说法冲突，说明各文档的观点\n\n# 用户问题\n\n[用户的问题]\n\n# 请回答\n\n</pre></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">关键要素</h5><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 明确&quot;仅基于文档&quot;的约束</li><li>• 提供&quot;无相关内容&quot;的处理方案</li><li>• 要求标注信息来源</li><li>• 处理文档冲突的情况</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/developer\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->开发者路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).pus